OL,3,CNHS trust admits liability for doctor
OL,4,Cwho sexually abused patients
OL,6,FThe Royal Cornwall Hospital Trust
OL,7,F(RCHT) has admitted liability and
OL,8,Fapologised after a doctor sexually
OL,9,Fabused patients.
OL,11,FDr Luliu Stan, who worked at the Royal
OL,12,FCornwall Hospital, was struck off the
OL,13,Fmedical register in 2024 after an
OL,14,Finvestigation by the General Medical
OL,15,FCouncil and a tribunal.
OL,17,FThe tribunal found he had subjected
OL,18,Fpatients to unnecessary intimate
OL,19,Fprocedures, including the
OL,20,Fadministration of rectal medication,
OL,21,Ffor his own sexual gratification.
