OL,3,CNHS trust admits liability for doctor
OL,4,Cwho sexually abused patients
OL,6,FA previous investigation by the Royal
OL,7,FCornwall Hospitals found Dr Stan had
OL,8,Fprescribed and administered rectal
OL,9,Fmedication on over 200 occasions -
OL,10,Fsometimes giving it to the same
OL,11,Fpatient multiple times.
OL,13,FDr Stan qualified in Romania in 2007.
OL,14,FHe was a Locum Senior House Officer in
OL,15,FTrauma and Orthopaedics for the Royal
OL,16,FCornwall Hospitals NHS Trust between
OL,17,F2017 and 2020.
