OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Royal Cornwall
OL,7,FHospital said: "We have written to
OL,8,Faffected individuals to admit
OL,9,Fliability for the actions of Dr Stan
OL,10,Fand to offer an unreserved apology to
OL,11,Fvictims.
OL,13,F"We are deeply sorry for the distress
OL,14,Fcaused by his serious professional
OL,15,Fmisconduct and his abuse of the trust
OL,16,Fplaced in him by patients.
