OL,6,F"Whilst we must follow due legal
OL,7,Fprocess, we will be doing everything
OL,8,Fwe can to bring investigations and
OL,9,Fclaims made by his victims to an early
OL,10,Fconclusion."
OL,12,FIn January 2024, a number of patients
OL,13,Fwere told by the Royal Cornwall
OL,14,FHospitals NHS Trust that details of
OL,15,Ftheir treatment would form part of the
OL,16,Ftribunal hearing.
