OL,3,CNHS trust admits liability for doctor
OL,4,Cwho sexually abused patients
OL,6,FIn July, the trust wrote to another
OL,7,Fgroup of former patients to tell them
OL,8,FDr Stan had given them rectal
OL,9,Fmedication when they were in hospital,
OL,10,Fand that in other cases the tribunal
OL,11,Fhad found his actions had been
OL,12,Fsexually motivated.
OL,14,FPeter, who wants to remain anonymous,
OL,15,Fwas one of the patients contacted in
OL,16,FJuly. He was treated by Dr Stan in the
OL,17,Femergency department of Royal Cornwall
OL,18,FHospital.
OL,20,FPeter said receiving that news by
OL,21,Fletter was "horrible" to deal with.
