OL,6,F"I have angry moments," he said. "I've
OL,7,Factually gone on to medication now to
OL,8,Ftry and numb it down a bit. It leaves
OL,9,Fyou angry, upset and it causes you a
OL,10,Flot of stress as well.
OL,12,F"I'm probably never going know what
OL,13,Factually happened, and I think that's
OL,14,Fgoing to be the hardest part to live
OL,15,Fwith."
