OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Royal Cornwall
OL,7,FHospitals NHS Trust said: "We would
OL,8,Furge any patient concerned about the
OL,9,Fcare they received from Dr Stan to
OL,10,Fcontact our team on
OL,11,Frcht.patientexperience@nhs.net.
OL,13,F"In addition to supporting patients,
OL,14,Fwe are working closely with
OL,15,Fsafeguarding services and the police
OL,16,Fregarding their ongoing enquiries into
OL,17,Fthe practice of Dr Stan."
